main event: A civilian reported seeing a bright, round object in the sky over Upper Darby, Pennsylvania on September 7, 1967.
interesting points: The object was described as bright white and the size of a quarter held at arm's length., The object moved in a zig-zag pattern while hovering high in the sky., The witness observed the object for approximately 2-3 minutes before it disappeared from view., The witness could not identify the object as an airplane or helicopter., The report remains unexplained and was forwarded to Project Blue Book for further evaluation.
